ygData.messageBody:
Well, in the spirit of sharing, I suppose it would be nice to have this
info. But I can agree that a strategy such as this, so successful, you
wouldn't want to tell the whole list. Could you give me a private e? I am
a 14th cleric, and am always scraping by. Any edge or hint would help. BTW,
I'm on the Rathe server, so unless you are on it too, I wouldn't affect your
profit.

Subject: RE: [EQ-Clerics] Dwarven Cleric


that is the thing I will not say....and the answer to why not is a good
reason. How many are on this list? how many are looking for ways to make a
quick buck? and how quickly would MY strategy on this be flooded if I was
to give it up?
